			<img alt="" src="/sites/default/files/imce/library-archives-rom2004_1306_31.jpg" style="width: 150px; float: left; height: 83px" /></td>
<td style="width: 450px; vertical-align: top">
<ul>
<li>hours: <span style="color: #b22222"><strong>Monday-Friday, 10 am-5 pm</strong></span></li>
<li>access: via Museum entrance on Bloor Street</li>
<li>collection focus:
<ul>
<li>historical documents relating to the Museum, including manuscripts and photographs</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
</td>
</tr>
